  "12b02efa-1cd8-4bd4-a1da-08449b6a265a"],
 "\nNotice how instead of going to the left and down, we go to the right and \
up. This means instead of the subtraction like in ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "1"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9c1eaad7-f7a7-478a-85bc-8dbea1fb8b70"],
 ", we need to add. Thus, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "5"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "adcf7f6e-a37d-489c-a5b5-7d1a16265292"],
 " is defined as the following:\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "5"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "eec60660-8589-4e7e-9833-bac0f8b41d3a"],
 " = ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "3"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8c474413-d9ec-465a-ba62-2e68baea9ff3"],
 " + (",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9a623b88-158d-46bd-91a0-e7b37ca16ee8"],
 "*cos(",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "lean"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "c75c291c-a3c5-491a-89b9-acd5e0c61a00"],
 "),",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d37111dc-244a-4057-ad6a-2e99d46a3dcc"],
 "*sin(",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "lean"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1ec97e5c-a59e-43b2-8ca0-f0eedbb821ca"],
 "))"
}], "Text",
