Using the Manipulate function to allow real-time input and simulation \
visualization for the model:\
\>", "CodeText",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9925119269338827`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"c77822b9-633a-485c-9639-\
2a5b42f8decc"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{" ", 
  RowBox[{"Manipulate", "[", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"drawMonkey2", "[", "thetaLean", "]"}], ",", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
